    },
    {
      "text": "Good performance in the capital markets boosted global ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 52.2,
      "w": 438.1,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "insurance industry total shareholder return (TSR) in 2023 ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 74.2,
      "w": 442.8,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "to 11%. However, five-year (2019–2023) TSR lags most ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 96.2,
      "w": 418.0,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "other industries, and over ten years the industry has mostly ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 118.2,
      "w": 460.8,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "delivered shareholder returns below the cost of equity",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 140.2,
      "w": 411.5,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "As a result, the industry has attracted less capital than ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 187.2,
      "w": 428.9,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "most industries over the past five years, losing share in ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 209.2,
      "w": 431.2,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "capital markets",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 231.2,
      "w": 120.4,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "Averages do not capture the diversity of performance ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 278.2,
      "w": 417.4,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "across the industry. About two-thirds of insurers have ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 300.2,
      "w": 417.3,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "generated TSR that exceeded their cost of equity, a ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 322.2,
      "w": 401.4,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "significant improvement over last year",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 344.2,
      "w": 297.1,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "Top-quartile insurers generated very substantial returns ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 391.2,
      "w": 437.0,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "for shareholders from 2019 through 2023, ranging from ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 413.1,
      "w": 431.5,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "16% to 44%, well above the all-industry TSR average of 9% ",
      "x": 692.1,
      "y": 435.1,
      "w": 457.8,
      "h": 23.4,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 18.0,
      "color": "#464547",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "Cash flow contribution and growth of tangible equity drove ",
